### Fetch blog data
GET http://localhost:3000/blog

### Fetch experience data
GET http://localhost:3000/experience

### Login to get JWT token
# @name login
POST http://localhost:3000/rpc/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Set token from login response
@token = {{login.response.body.token}}

### Fetch a specific row by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/blog?id=eq.1

### Fetch rows with a filter (e.g., title contains 'test')
GET http://localhost:3000/blog?title=like.*test*

### Insert a new blog post (requires authentication)
POST http://localhost:3000/blog
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "My Second Blog Post",
  "body": "This is the content of my first blog post."
}